net.commotionwireless.shell
Class ShellProcess

java.lang.Object
  net.commotionwireless.shell.ShellProcess

public class ShellProcess
extends java.lang.Object

ShellProcess represents a process running in a fork shell (which itself is represented as a Shell.)
